# Figma Target File

- All components carried to the Figma canvas in this project must be created or updated in the `Figma MCP Testing` file.
- Use this file as the target:
  - `https://www.figma.com/design/nPIzAMiRIezs04KU8kxrTF/Figma-MCP-Testing?node-id=0-1&t=S1gcyCuYVErJDrRB-1`
- Treat file key `nPIzAMiRIezs04KU8kxrTF` as the default target unless the user explicitly overrides it.
- If a request appears to target a different file and the user has not clearly approved that change, pause and ask with `AskQuestion`.
